track_notes: From the mountain station of Koninki chair lift. Track includes a visit at the Turbacz hut (Schronisko PTTK)

This is the track of an activation walk by SQ9OZM, G4OBK and GI4ONL in April 2016. We spent considerable time on the two summits activating on HF and also time in the mountain hut eating and drinking (one beer) at lunchtime on BZ-005. I recommended this walk unreservedly!
